title: Georges Seurat A Sunday on La Grande Jatte—1884 Eyeglass Case with Cloth
description:
Eyeglass Case developed from Georges Seurat’s A Sunday on La Grande Jatte—1884, 1884-86, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

This sturdy hard shell eyeglass case also includes a matching microfiber lens cloth. 

  • Dimensions: Glass Case: 6.25 x 2.25 x 1.25 in. Cloth: 6 x7 in.
  • Materials: Plastic, microfiber.
